    <item>
      <title>据当地媒体报道，印尼将把一年的出口收入转回国内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地新闻媒体 Kontan 援引一位高级部长的话报道，印尼将要求自然资源出口商将部分外汇收入在境内保留至少一年，以增加外汇储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喜力印度分公司停止向关键邦销售啤酒，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/heineken-s-india-unit-stops-beer-sales-to-key-state-shares-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[喜力啤酒公司印度分公司暂停向印度南部特伦甘纳邦供应啤酒，理由是价格无利可图且未能付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/heineken-s-india-unit-stops-beer-sales-to-key-state-shares-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌预计 2024 年天然气收益将下降，因业绩不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司表示，其天然气部门的销售量和交易收入均有所下降，这是表明 2024 年对于主要能源公司来说将以疲软的业绩结束的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
